- Pokertanje dockera na root putanji repozitorijuma gde se nalazi docker file
  *Mora da bude pokrenut Docker Desktop app
docker-compose -f docker-compose.dev.yml up

- Bildovanje dokera, gde se pokrece u pozadini iako pise done.
docker-compose -f docker-compose.dev.yml up --build -d

- Pokretanje mongodb shell
    Commands to start:
        docker-compose up -d

    Commands to stop:
        docker-compose down

    Commands to run CLI via container:
        docker exec -it mongo bash

        mongo --username root --password password --authenticationDatabase admin





- Gasenje dockera nakon ctrl+c (Izlazak sa mongo servera)
docker-compose -f docker-compose.dev.yml down 


- Brisanje volume (Memorije kontejnera)
 docker volume prune

* Dokumentacija Docker command
https://docs.docker.com/engine/reference/commandline/docker/